        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>textile weaving techniques by patterning [300232046], textile weaving processes and techniques [300245451], textile construction processes and techniques [300239729], textile processes and techniques [300239669], processes and techniques by material [300053900], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
